Ang sarsa na ito ay ang perpektong proporsyon.

613
00:36:47,747 --> 00:36:49,040
Ang strawberry jam talaga ang pinakamasarap.

614
00:36:49,207 --> 00:36:50,458
May taste ka.

615
00:36:50,542 --> 00:36:52,210
- Hoy, Kang Seong-jae.
- Pribadong Unang Klase Kang Seong-jae.

616
00:36:52,293 --> 00:36:55,130
Kaya, nakakatulong ba si Kim Kwan-cheol?

617
00:36:56,005 --> 00:36:57,006
